game.name: Park My Truck
game.description:
If you have bored of too much speed and racing game, then truck parking game  -  Park My Truck is the game, where, your steering guts can be checked out. In this online parking game under the multiple level games a player has to park at the allotted spot in the vehicle. However, in this racing game you have to achieve this objective without damaging the vehicle that you are driving towards the parking space.

Though, to caution you damage meter is being always displayed there so that you must carefully park your vehicle. The exciting and absolutely exceptional for this free parking games is provision of an opportunity to check the hand eye co-ordination and spatial reasoning skill of yours?. This makes and keep a player? interest intact in playing Park My Truck game. The expert maneuvering of fingers in and the tasks accomplished within permissible time limit and situations in order to reach at the next level are too important in this online racing game for free.

In each of the level of the game, the simulation level you will found to be varying. Sometimes you will have to park in the public place, whereas, in the mode it will be secluded parking space for the game.
